  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\r\n\r\n- [X] Foundry\r\n- [ ] Foundryup\r\n\r\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\r\n\r\nforge 0.2.0 (7278695 2022-08-27T00:10:44.256931Z)\r\n\r\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\r\n\r\nforge build\r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\n\r\nmacOS (Intel)\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nThe default repo generated by `forge init`:\r\n```\r\n$ forge build\r\n[⠢] Compiling...\r\n[⠢] Compiling 9 files with 0.8.16\r\n[⠔] Solc 0.8.16 finished in 1.95s\r\nCompiler run successful\r\n$ forge build\r\n[⠔] Compiling...\r\nNo files changed, compilation skipped\r\n```\r\n\r\nMy repo https://github.com/minaminao/ctf-blockchain (e.g., commit: 82dcc110e4da3a6c696e0ca70f0ee3f6642ad8f1):\r\n```\r\n$ forge build\r\nMissing dependencies found. Installing now.\r\n\r\n[⠘] Compiling...\r\n[⠃] Compiling 2 files with 0.5.17\r\n[⠊] Compiling 14 files with 0.7.6\r\n[⠢] Compiling 241 files with 0.8.16\r\n[⠢] Solc 0.5.17 finished in 37.96ms\r\n[⠑] Solc 0.7.6 finished in 2.03s\r\n[⠘] Solc 0.8.16 finished in 17.86s\r\nCompiler run successful (with warnings)\r\n\r\n(warnings)\r\n\r\n$ forge build\r\n[⠔] Compiling...\r\n[⠑] Compiling 95 files with 0.8.16\r\n[⠃] Solc 0.8.16 finished in 17.64s\r\nCompiler run successful (with warnings)\r\n\r\n(warnings)\r\n\r\n$ forge build\r\n[⠑] Compiling...\r\n[⠃] Compiling 101 files with 0.8.16\r\n[⠢] Solc 0.8.16 finished in 18.62s\r\nCompiler run successful (with warnings)\r\n\r\n(warnings)\r\n\r\n$ forge build\r\n[⠔] Compiling...\r\n[⠆] Compiling 6 files with 0.7.6\r\n[⠃] Solc 0.7.6 finished in 1.72s\r\nCompiler run successful\r\n```\r\n\r\nAs shown above, the recompilation runs even though no files have been changed, and the target files to be recompiled are different each time.\r\nI do not know the cause of this problem.",
